message.text:
Ready for many years of adventures! ü´∂

The Maxi-Cosi Nomad XL Plus is perfect for travelling with your little one, not only is it compact & collapsible, it can be used from toddler stage up to 12 years old ü•∞

It is really simple to transform the seat for the next stage so you can continue using the seat for many adventures to come ‚úàÔ∏è 

#maxicosi #nomadcarseat #travelcarseat #carseatsafety #carseats #highbackedboosterseat #boosterseat
